This year, 2018, we target a capitalization of USD. 5 million which will help us reach approximately USD. 10m in revenues. The investors can exit quarterly taking 5% interest monthly for short term (1 year) investors or wait to exit at end of term for long term (5 year) investors taking 10x return on investment. Our team is comprised of three full time employees, part time contract agents, a board, outsourced consultants, advisors, and interns.
